race.comment: Very competitive. MONTEZULU (5) is going better than it looks and has been close to the winner in all four runs this time in. Has placed 3/3 course and distance and aided by the claimer again. Expected to go close. TASSIE POWER (6) is yet another overdue for a win. Has placed three of four starts since a win five back. Beaten in a three way photo last time when trying to lead throughout and will give a sight again. SOUTH GEORGIA (9) is fitter for two runs back and after being beaten a head fresh was a fast finishing third last time. Well weighted with the claim and looks a leading chance with further improvement. RUBBLEONTHEDOUBLE (1) has been racing well over further rand in tougher races. Tricky gate and back in trip but this easier and should be in the finish.
